Titolo: The Final Conflict (video game)

Anno: 1982

Descrizione: The Final Conflict is a strategy game written by Thomas G. Cleaver for the Apple II and published by Hayden Software in 1982. An Atari 8-bit family version followed in 1983. In The Final Conflict,  the human race has met its demise. What remains are the ruins of dead civilizations and two robot armies, loyal to the whims of their expired human creators.